ğŸš€ TaskFlow Studio

A modern web-based project management application designed to streamline team collaboration, task tracking, and project organization through an intuitive and responsive interface.

Developed during my Web Development Internship at Optimus Technocrates (India) Pvt. Ltd..

ğŸ“Œ Overview

TaskFlow Studio simplifies project and task management by enabling teams to:

Create and manage multiple projects

Assign and track tasks with priority levels

Monitor project progress in real time

Collaborate efficiently through role-based access

Maintain transparency with structured workflows

The application follows modern frontend architecture and integrates seamlessly with backend services using RESTful APIs.

